snippet.textDisplay: Universal healthcare is not the answer. When you have a severe illness wait times are not acceptable. This is the first time in history we had this much problems with healthcare and all the sudden its considered terrible? The affordable care act, Medicaid, Government subs, extreme regulations (10 year medical trials), are mainly what sabotaged our system.
